Quick Reference
Read -&gt; Decode -&gt; Use
TBmpImage img;
tbmp_open(buf, len, &amp;img);

TBmpFrame frame = { .pixels = malloc(w*h*4) };
tbmp_decode(&amp;img, &amp;frame);

// use frame.pixels...

